author: HBO Max
description:
Join James Gunn and co-hosts Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt) & Steve Agee (John Economos) for the official Peacemaker podcast. In this episode, they break down Season 1, Ep 2 (“Best Friends For Never”) with special guest Robert Patrick (Auggie Smith), sharing behind-the-scenes stories, laughs & DCU insights. In this episode, the team dives into emotional character arcs, hilarious set stories, and how key scenes came together. Hear never-before-shared insights about Chris Smith's evolution, Auggie’s twisted role in the story, and what it was like filming during the early days of the series. New episodes drop Mondays and Thursdays. Stream Peacemaker on HBO Max and follow along with the podcast.
